name: Blueberry Cough
description: Blueberry Cough is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Blueberry and Strawberry Cough. This strain is 50% sativa and 50% indica. Blueberry Cough is 15% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Bred by unknown breeders, the average price of Blueberry Cough typically ranges from $10-$15 per gram.
